      "description": "## Overview\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Inefficient Algorithmic Complexity via the `BinEncoder` process. An attacker can cause excessive CPU consumption by sending specially crafted messages with numerous records that trigger repeated linear scans for name compression candidates.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `hickory-proto` to version 0.26.1 or higher.\n## References\n- [GitHub Advisory](https://github.com/hickory-dns/hickory-dns/security/advisories/GHSA-q2qq-hmj6-3wpp)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/hickory-dns/hickory-dns/commit/6e70e931515286a701b00ce91b06988eb71e89ef)\n- [GitHub Release](https://github.com/hickory-dns/hickory-dns/releases/tag/v0.26.1)\n- [RustSec Advisory](https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2026-0119.html)\n",
